title: Ebro In The Morning - Texas Shooting & Gun Violence + Brandy Freestyles Over Jack Harlow's "First Class"
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 5/25/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio breaking down the recent tragedy in Texas, Brandy clapping back over Jack Harlow's "First Class," and play White-Ish Wednesday.
